            <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="headline">CRS Score for Canada PR 2026 – What Minimum CRS Score Do You Need?</h1>
            <p class="post-lead" itemprop="description">The Comprehensive Ranking System (CRS) determines who receives a Canada PR Invitation to Apply (ITA) through Express Entry. This guide explains exactly what CRS score you need for Canada PR in 2026 — by draw type, program, and province.</p>

